  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/7a9b2d3391a0cea459de10a122c6f95b.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In a world plunged into turmoil and instability, two rival clans, the S.S.C. and Eclipse, vie for dominance.   <br>  <br>The troubled town of Havenport, seemingly on the brink of serious conflict, calls upon a skilled fighter to uncover Eclipse's mysterious plans and put a stop to them before it's too late.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/8933a652ceed8728dc5e7806aa2947af.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Put up your dukes and battle foes using a uniquely fast-paced, punch-and-dodge combat system. Choose to play aggressively or defensively to overcome ever-mounting challenges.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/269dccf1974aa8af02bf605190acbf08.poster.avif?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/269dccf1974aa8af02bf605190acbf08.webm?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/269dccf1974aa8af02bf605190acbf08.mp4?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Attack enemies when they become vulnerable</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quickly defend against incoming attacks</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind your stamina and battle tactfully</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use items to aid yourself or hinder opponents  </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/d25bf753bf0f31dad7428bb73f4929e8.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the town of Havenport and meet a wide assortment of friends and foes alike. Uncover Havenport's secrets and collect items to aid you in combat.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/aee39f6c1c441e0ab2df3488cfe34628.poster.avif?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/aee39f6c1c441e0ab2df3488cfe34628.webm?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/aee39f6c1c441e0ab2df3488cfe34628.mp4?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interact with characters in the overworld</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be thorough and explore for unique secrets and interactions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect and purchase combat items and costumes  </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/96f82ec511597d934c1d206b361369e3.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hone your skills, assist a friend in need, or just take a load off with an array of engaging minigames and side-quests. Besting these challenges will net you various rewards and coins useful for unlocking additional content, items, and aesthetics!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/18d1b943d0b0ae3619801703485dce2b.poster.avif?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/18d1b943d0b0ae3619801703485dce2b.webm?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/18d1b943d0b0ae3619801703485dce2b.mp4?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete special tasks</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn rewards</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock challenging post-game content  </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/d81eb7eba6e41bf838339246338c8dd2.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Havenport, nothing comes easy, and not everything is as it seems. Follow an intriguing, developing storyline rife with a complex history, opposing forces, and surprises around every corner.<br><br>People need a hero, and it's time to answer their call!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/7a9b2d3391a0cea459de10a122c6f95b.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In a world plunged into turmoil and instability, two rival clans, the S.S.C. and Eclipse, vie for dominance.   <br>  <br>The troubled town of Havenport, seemingly on the brink of serious conflict, calls upon a skilled fighter to uncover Eclipse's mysterious plans and put a stop to them before it's too late.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/8933a652ceed8728dc5e7806aa2947af.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Put up your dukes and battle foes using a uniquely fast-paced, punch-and-dodge combat system. Choose to play aggressively or defensively to overcome ever-mounting challenges.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/269dccf1974aa8af02bf605190acbf08.poster.avif?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/269dccf1974aa8af02bf605190acbf08.webm?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/269dccf1974aa8af02bf605190acbf08.mp4?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Attack enemies when they become vulnerable</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quickly defend against incoming attacks</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind your stamina and battle tactfully</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use items to aid yourself or hinder opponents  </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/d25bf753bf0f31dad7428bb73f4929e8.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the town of Havenport and meet a wide assortment of friends and foes alike. Uncover Havenport's secrets and collect items to aid you in combat.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/aee39f6c1c441e0ab2df3488cfe34628.poster.avif?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/aee39f6c1c441e0ab2df3488cfe34628.webm?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/aee39f6c1c441e0ab2df3488cfe34628.mp4?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interact with characters in the overworld</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be thorough and explore for unique secrets and interactions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect and purchase combat items and costumes  </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/96f82ec511597d934c1d206b361369e3.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hone your skills, assist a friend in need, or just take a load off with an array of engaging minigames and side-quests. Besting these challenges will net you various rewards and coins useful for unlocking additional content, items, and aesthetics!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/18d1b943d0b0ae3619801703485dce2b.poster.avif?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/18d1b943d0b0ae3619801703485dce2b.webm?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/18d1b943d0b0ae3619801703485dce2b.mp4?t=1754630830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete special tasks</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn rewards</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock challenging post-game content  </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376060/extras/d81eb7eba6e41bf838339246338c8dd2.webp?t=1754630830\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Havenport, nothing comes easy, and not everything is as it seems. Follow an intriguing, developing storyline rife with a complex history, opposing forces, and surprises around every corner.<br><br>People need a hero, and it's time to answer their call!</strong></p>",
